        <updateDate>2018-06-27T13:45:55Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing Opioids and Unused Narcotics with Deliberate Disposal and Packaging Act of 2018 or the SOUND Disposal and Packaging Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to authorize the Food and Drug Administration to require certain packaging and disposal technologies, controls, or measures to mitigate the risk of abuse or misuse of a drug or a class of drugs.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
